{"tid":141832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆乳熟女牙助兼差　爽吃3足球隊未成年學生","createTime":"2017-03-03T08:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T11:31:39.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24fb3aa732b37daa11bb47c3620335854199b590","tid":141832,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:54:40.000Z","msg":"美國經常傳出「女大男小」發生關係的新聞。美國加州日前一名42歲熟女遭逮捕，原因是與3名未成年學生做愛。不過，這次並不是師生戀，而是足球隊的攝影師，案情會曝光也是由教職員舉報。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，爆乳熟女弗萊徹（Mary Fletcher）平時在牙醫診所當助理，但閒暇時間也會到學校的足球隊當隨隊攝影師，也因為這層關係認識了3名未成年男學生。她先後與這3名學生發生關係；由於教職員察覺不對勁，案情才曝光。<br />\n<br />\n警方2016年9月獲報開啟調查，直到上月28號才將弗萊徹逮捕；檢方也指出，目前還未發現有老師或行政人員涉案。本案將於22日開庭審理，弗萊徹目前已交保，等候開庭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2368/d2368548.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2368%2Fd2368548.jpg&h=541fc304&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"049edf2840147032dde937e69af0e53f7dd9550e","tid":141832,"uid":42755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"快來強姦我吧"},{"pid":"0a58b68f4ee2e18c9dcf350b2077083e634558ec","tid":141832,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:57:05.000Z","msg":"我絕對有講過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99d7295ae816a98ff502d81137656cf217895ea","tid":141832,"uid":42550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我絕對有講過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e9ffaf6d26f77d4e5630bf118eeffb8cdc4220","tid":141832,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:59:25.000Z","msg":"MILF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53